name: Synergy
description: XSULLO (visuals) BOOTS (audio). BOOTS is a 2x Grammy Nominated artist, record producer singer/songwriter. He came to prominence after producing Beyoncé's critically acclaimed self-titled fifth studio album, and he’s worked closely with FKA twigs, Run the Jewels, Jay Z, among others. XSULLO & BOOTS friendship began in 2017 while collaborating on various projects. They both draw from similar inspirations and visions, and felt a natural gravitational pull to come together on a collaborative NFT experience. In “Synergy” the viewer witnesses two transdimensional beings colliding into existence; emerging deep from the primordial realm & engulfed between the outer & inner. Forever locked in an eternal loop, soundtracked by a lush dreamscape. This work is part of the,Dart2121 exhibition. From the 23rd of November 2021 to the 6th of February 2022, Milan - Dart Museum - Permanente di Milano - Wrong Theory
